title: land sale Weeraketiya Pasman Handiya
details: Weeraketiya, Pasman Handia, Ranna Parata muhunala Deveni ela laga pehita athi mema perches 19.8 bumiya nevasak sadaha sudusu isthanayaki, Nala jalaya, Thekala veduliya, Sinnakkara oppu, Pradesiya shabava anumath peburu path, Varipanam ankaya sahitha Nagara semave pehita athi thanithala polava,
